                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.113/9307: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Summerlin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-03-07T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 7, 1922—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>34. Your 32, March 6, 5 p.m. Department has today made public that embargo will
                    not be renewed at this time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
